install Wazuh Manager (Linux)....
Login to Ubuntu server
Update system:
sudo apt update
sudo apt upgrade -y

Install required packages:
sudo apt install curl apt-transport-https unzip lsb-release gnupg -y

Download Wazuh installation script:
curl -sO https://packages.wazuh.com/4.7/wazuh-install.sh

Run installation:
sudo bash wazuh-install.sh -a

This installs:
Wazuh Manager
Elasticsearch
Kibana Dashboard

After installation you will get:
Dashboard URL
Username : admin
Password : ********

Access dashboard:
https://192.168.1.10
